values:
AMERICA, FUCK YEAH
Not gonna lie, I teared up out of sheer joy. And I never cry out of happiness; the only times I ever did so was during my high school reunion and the finale of the OC. :') To think that my vote for my first presidential election helped bring us to these amazing results - although, he won way before California's ballots were tallied. Gaaaah, yes we can! I have never been so proud to be American, and I have never been so proud of my country. President Obama!
